name: 5pmSomewhere
0:
”Alexa, open five PM.”
”Is it five PM anywhere?”
”Where is it five PM?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: five p. m.
des: The last time someone told you "it's 5 PM somewhere," did you wonder where that somewhere was? Alexa will happily answer that question for you.
